        "client_msg_id": "e48e0fa4-fdf6-446b-87b5-07e30d603f2b",
        "text": "I'm reading _Hild_ [1] right now which is a work of historical fiction set in 7th century Britain. The noble women are all into weaving and plotting politics. And their metaphors for the most subtle politics all involve weaving. Makes me realize the extent to which weaving was the sophisticated technology of a long era.\n\n[1] As an aside, highly recommended: <https:\/\/www.goodreads.com\/book\/show\/17332243-hild|https:\/\/www.goodreads.com\/book\/show\/17332243-hild>",
