        "client_msg_id": "0d5c31e8-dfbc-43fd-8ae8-3d235b95c31a",
        "text": "<https:\/\/youtu.be\/dGvG2wCTJK8?si=0JecFvpLgqZX5iLX|https:\/\/youtu.be\/dGvG2wCTJK8?si=0JecFvpLgqZX5iLX>\nWhoa.  Similar to <@U03R0B9U1GD>'s probabilistic rule-driven VMs,\nplus a touch of Orca?  (Specifically the way the kid _built_ a timer out of a character pacing back and forth, see around 11:10-14:30)\nI particularly love the use of user-drawn icons in lieu of symbols.  Naming is hard (and requires literacy).",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
